{"article_id":"W5w4Id82hy8bU3HI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Republican lawmakers have finally unveiled a plan","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to repeal major portions of Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"capping years of attacks against the health care law and a months-long debate","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that exposed deep rifts within the GOP .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"House Republican leaders must begin in earnest the tough task","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"of selling the new plan","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"to overhaul America 's health care system","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to colleagues in both chambers on Capitol Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"where there is a myriad of clashing interests .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"And they will have to convince a skeptical public","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"it 's worthwhile ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"just seven years after Congress passed the Affordable Care Act .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The political ramifications could n't be more significant .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Perceptions","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that Republicans and President Donald Trump are not moving ahead with a wholesale Obamacare repeal","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"would anger large swaths of the party 's base ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"while the possibility","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"of millions of Americans losing coverage","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"could emerge as a top liability for Republicans ahead of the 2018 midterm elections .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Trump is expected to offer a more robust embrace of the House GOP health care plan Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"when he meets with the deputy whip team at the White House in the afternoon ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"an administration official told CNN Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Whether Trump is committed to the political challenge","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"of repealing and replacing Obamacare","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"remains a central question .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"`` He 'll work hard","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to get this done , ''","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the administration official said ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"including pushing reluctant conservatives","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"by helping build support for this bill out in their districts .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"That 's one of the reasons","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Texas Sen. Ted Cruz was invited to the White House for dinner Wednesday night .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"He 's among the skeptical conservatives","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"who believe","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"the new bill is essentially a new mandate .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"In the coming days , key House committees will hold extended sessions","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"to debate and revise a bill","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that until Monday night was closely guarded","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"- including being held in a House office","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"for lawmakers to view but not copy .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"These gatherings will provide plenty of opportunity for political grandstanding from Democrats","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"as they look to cast Republicans as responsible","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"for taking away people 's health insurance .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"The legislation","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"unveiled Monday","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"would scrap the individual mandate , a major pillar of Obamacare ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"replacing it with refundable tax credits for individuals","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to purchase health insurance .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"It would also restructure Medicaid","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and defund Planned Parenthood .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The proposal","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"-- dubbed the `` American Health Care Act '' --","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"seeks to maintain Obamacare 's protections for people with pre-existing conditions ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"but would allow insurers to charge higher premiums to individuals","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"whose coverage has lapsed .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The bill would also keep in place the so-called `` Cadillac tax '' on employers","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"who provide generous health insurance plans .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Americans are virtually split on the individual mandate ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"with 48 % favoring removing the requirement","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to obtain coverage","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"or pay a penalty","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and 50 % wanting to keep it ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"according to a CNN/ORC poll","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"released Tuesday morning .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Other aspects of Obamacare are far more popular .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"A broad majority , 87 % , support maintaining the law 's protections for those with pre-existing conditions ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"and 61 % are opposed to a replacement bill","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that would curb funding for the expansion of the Medicaid program .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Here are the political obstacles","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Republican leaders are about to confront","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"as they attempt to get this bill through the House and Senate .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"The real-world ramifications","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"of repealing Obamacare","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"are complicated","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to say the least .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"But most health care experts agree on this much :","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Millions of Americans are likely to lose their coverage under the new GOP plan .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"It will be a tough pill for many Americans to swallow seven years after the passage of the Affordable Care Act .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The law has been highly controversial since its inception ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"but the reality is that some 20 million people gained coverage","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"as a result of it","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"-- particularly low-income Americans .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"The most prominent Republican has already veered off-message on this front :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Trump .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"While Trump wants to eliminate Obamacare ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"the President frustrated his colleagues","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"when he promised earlier this year","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"that the GOP plan would offer `` insurance for everybody . ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Tevi Troy , deputy secretary of Health and Human Services under President George W. Bush , said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"the GOP 's top challenge is `` meeting the expectations '' on coverage .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"`` They need to maintain coverage levels","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"so you wo n't have large numbers of people","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"saying ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"' I was covered under Obamacare","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and I 'm not covered now , ' ''","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"Troy told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The changes","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that House Republicans are proposing to make to Medicaid","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"are not sitting well","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"-- among some fellow Republicans .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Thirty-one states expanded Medicaid under the Affordable Care Act ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"extending coverage to some 11 million low-income adults .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Drastically restricting that program would leave many of those people without coverage","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"-- an outcome","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"that has plenty of GOP governors and lawmakers on edge .","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"The plan would overhaul the whole program ,","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"which covers more than 70 million people ,","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"by sending states a fixed amount of money per enrollee ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"known as a per-capita cap .","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"GOP Sen. Lisa Murkowski said","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"that her party must find a `` fair and humane '' way","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"to treat those","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"who gained coverage through Medicaid expansion .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"`` In Alaska , we 've got 27,000 people","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"that are now eligible for coverage","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"that did n't have it before .","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"Really have no place else","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"to turn , ''","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"Murkowski said .","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"`` And so I 'm trying to figure out a way","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"that treats these people in a fair and humane manner . ''","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch , the top Republican on the Senate Finance Committee , said","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"the intra-party division over Medicaid was a `` problem . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"`` The Democrats are n't going to help us .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"So it is a problem , ''","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Hatch told reporters","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"moments before the House bill was released .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Their concern :","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"The proposal does n't go far enough","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"in gutting Obamacare .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Over the past few weeks , GOP lawmakers like Sen. Rand Paul and members of the conservative House Freedom Caucus have raised hell over the draft bill ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"and it became clear Monday night that one provision","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"they railed against","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"-- refundable tax credits --","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"remains in the final draft .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Conservatives say","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"the refundable tax credits amount to just another entitlement program .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"`` Still have not seen an official version of the House Obamacare replacement bill ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"but from media reports","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"this sure looks like Obamacare Lite ! ''","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"Paul tweeted Monday night .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Analysis on the bill circulated by staff for the Republican Study Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"a group of fiscal conservatives zeroed in on the tax credits ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"referring to them as `` a Republican welfare entitlement '' `` Writing checks to individuals","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"to purchase insurance","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"is , in principle , Obamacare , ''","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"‎ the RSC memo","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":", obtained from a GOP source","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":", stated","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":". Meanwhile , conservatives may also have problems with other provisions of the bill , like the fa","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"t that the House plan wo n't scrap the Obamacare taxes until 20","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"8 or the fa","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"t it preserves the Cadillac T","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"x -- which has never been implemented","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"- yet still has been a point of contention for Democrats and Republicans alike","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":". Freedom Caucus member Rep. Jim Jordan sa","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"d cited specific frustration with the fa","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"t that the House bill would keep Obamacare taxes in place until 20","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"8 instead of repealing them immediate","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"y like a 2015 repeal and replacement measu","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"e vetoed by President Barack Oba","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"a would have done","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":". `` We put on President Obama 's desk a bi","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"l that got rid of all the tax","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"s and ... a Republican Congress is going to put on a Republican president 's desk a bi","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"l that keeps taxes in place ? '","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"' Jordan , R-Ohio , said","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":". House GOP leaders can only lose roughly 20 Republican vot","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"s when the bill comes to the floor later this month","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":". Conservatives are under pressure from outside advocacy groups like Heritage Action and the Club for Grow","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"h and will be reluctant to support the bi","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"l unless their major areas of concern are addressed","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":". `` The real deba","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"e going on between the House G","depth":16},{"id":175,"text":"P is membe","depth":17},{"id":176,"text":"s who want to make substantial changes to the A","depth":18},{"id":177,"text":"A but reali","depth":19},{"id":178,"text":"e getting rid of it will be quite problemat","depth":19},{"id":179,"text":"c and membe","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"s who ... generally want to get rid of everythi","depth":18},{"id":181,"text":"g and go back to the w","depth":19},{"id":182,"text":"y things were , '","depth":19},{"id":183,"text":"' said Andy Slavitt , former acting head of the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":". `` It 's not possible . '","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"' Over the course of the last few weeks , committee staff have gone back and forth with the Congressional Budget Office","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":". While there was no official score","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":", sources s","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"y the early returns for CBO were n't positi","depth":16},{"id":189,"text":"e -- both in cost and in coverage","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":". Many of the prominent shifts in the bill 's language , in fact , were driven by GOP effor","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"s to secure a better final score","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":", sources said","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":". House GOP leaders have coordinated with their Senate counterpar","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"s and insi","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"t they are largely all on the same page","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":". But House Speaker Ryan and Senate Majority Leader McConnell face different internal dynamics in their chambers","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":", and a bi","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"l that can pass in the Hou","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"e is not necessarily a bi","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"l that can pass the Senate","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":". One potential holdup in the Senate will be over funding Planned Parenthood","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":". Many House conservatives and outside groups are worri","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"d that in the upper chamber","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":", where Republicans hold a narrow majority","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":", leaders will be forced to strip out the provisi","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"n to defund the gro","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"p to get support of more centrist GOP senators like Susan Collins of Maine","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":". Another iss","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"e that has split Senate and House Republica","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"s is the proposed overhaul of the Medicaid program","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":". Even before the House bill was released","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":", four Senate Republica","depth":12},{"id":213,"text":"s -- Murkowski , Rob Portman of Ohio , Shelly Moore Capito of West Virginia , and Cory Gardner of Colorado","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"- of penned a letter to McConne","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"l expressing concer","depth":12},{"id":216,"text":"s that the legislation would cut off tho","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"e relying on Medica","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"d to address opioid addiction and mental health issues","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":". JUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"D Rubio not insisting on full Obamacare repe","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"l Replay More Videos .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":". MUST WAT","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"H Rubio not insisting on full Obamacare repe","depth":11},{"id":224,"text":"l 01:","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"3 `` We belie","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"e Medicaid needs to be reformed","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":", but reform should not come at the cost of disruption in access to health care for our country 's most vulnerable and sickest individuals , '","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"' the senators wrote","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":". House GOP aides point to the provisi","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"n that grandfathers existing enrolle","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"s and allows them to keep their coverage","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":". But it 's unclear if the details in the House bill will address these concerns","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":", which have the potenti","depth":11},{"id":234,"text":"l to derail the bi","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"l as it works its way through the legislative process","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":". House Republican leaders will need all the he","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"p they can get in the coming wee","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"s as they try to shepherd their Obamacare bill through Congress","depth":8},{"id":239,"text":". It 's not clear whether that support will come from the White House","depth":8},{"id":240,"text":". House GOP aides have repeatedly claim","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"d they are working `` hand in glove '' with the White House","depth":11},{"id":242,"text":", and over the course of the final harried days of drafting , that was true","depth":10},{"id":243,"text":". There was deep involvement of several top executive branch officials over the weekend","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":". `` House just introduced the bi","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"l to # RepealAndReplace # Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":246,"text":". Ti","depth":8},{"id":247,"text":"e to end this nightmare , '","depth":8},{"id":248,"text":"' the message said","depth":6},{"id":249,"text":". Meanwhile , White House spokesman Sean Spicer said in a statement Monday nig","depth":7},{"id":250,"text":"t that the House bill was an `` important step '","depth":8},{"id":251,"text":"' in fixing the health care syst","depth":8},{"id":252,"text":"m -- but did not go as far as to offer a explicit or forceful backing","depth":6},{"id":253,"text":". And Tuesday morning , Trump was still qualifying his support for `` our bill , '","depth":6},{"id":254,"text":"' sayi","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"g it was out for `` review and negotiation . '","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":511,"left":0,"right":510,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":510,"left":298,"right":509,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":290,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":274,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":267,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":259,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":257,"right":258,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":263,"right":265,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":261,"right":262,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":5,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":264,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":273,"left":13,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":269,"right":271,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":268,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":19,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":270,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":284,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":279,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":276,"right":278,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":275,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":277,"right":25,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":277,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":281,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":28,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":285,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":33,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":294,"right":296,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":36,"right":293,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":37,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":38,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":41,"right":295,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":509,"left":472,"right":508,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":472,"left":322,"right":471,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":311,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":304,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":302,"right":303,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":302,"left":299,"right":301,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":46,"right":300,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":310,"left":308,"right":309,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":306,"right":307,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":305,"right":53,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":317,"right":320,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":317,"left":58,"right":316,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":316,"left":314,"right":3